data.description: Oversized 4 unit multifamily located in Humboldt Park. This building has a brick exterior with two entrances that sits on a corner lot. The owners units features hardwood floors and custom blinds with a formal dining room.   Some work was started in the building but is is incomplete.   Bring your vision and your ideas to rehab the property. This property is being sold as-is.  Bring us an offer!!
